descriptionNullable:
This is the revised dataset based on the Excel file from [tableau.com](https://community.tableau.com/s/question/0D54T00000CWeX8SAL/sample-superstore-sales-excelxls), which includes the sales data for a superstore from January 2014 to December 2017 (4 years' data).

This dataset can be used to learn time series analysis, cohort analysis, etc.
